#: content/announcements/gear/22.04.0.md:112
msgid "And also this..."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/announcements/gear/22.04.0.md:114
msgid "[Elisa](https://elisa.kde.org/), KDE's elegant and modern music player, improves its support for touch screens, is faster, more stable and you can now drag and drop music and playlist files from your file manager onto the playlist panel."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/announcements/gear/22.04.0.md:115
msgid "With [Skanpage](https://apps.kde.org/skanpage/), KDE's scanning utility, you can now share scanned documents (including multi-page PDFs) using KDE's general sharing system, which allows you to push documents to instant messaging apps, online cloud services, social services, and through Bluetooth to other devices."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/announcements/gear/22.04.0.md:116
msgid "[Spectacle](https://apps.kde.org/spectacle/)'s annotation tools add functionality to crop, scale, undo, redo, and in general do many more things with the images you screenshot. Also, any annotation settings you change will be remembered the next time you startup the program."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/announcements/gear/22.04.0.md:117
msgid "[Gwenview](https://apps.kde.org/gwenview/), KDE's image viewer, detects and guides you through the installation of camera importers that are lacking support packages. There is also a new *Print Preview* functionality for when you need a hard copy."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/announcements/gear/22.04.0.md:118
msgid "[KDE Itinerary](https://apps.kde.org/itinerary/), KDE's travel assistant (also available for your phone), improves support for more train companies (such as Renfe and Amtrak) and airlines. It also adds more detailed information for weather and an inbuilt barcode scanner so you can scan your ticket's information directly from the app."
msgstr ""

