#. +> trunk5
#: content/announcements/gear/22.08.0.md:40
msgid "KDE Gear ‚öôÔ∏è is the collection of KDE apps, frameworks and libraries that all release new versions at the same time. Version 22.08 brings updates for KDE programs for working, developing your creativity and enjoying your free time without having to submit yourself to extortionate licenses, intrusive advertising, or surrender your privacy."
