#: content/announcements/gear/22.12.0.md:40
msgid "KDE Gear ‚öôÔ∏è is back with exciting new features, performance boosts, and bugfixes for all your favorite KDE apps!"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/announcements/gear/22.12.0.md:42
msgid "In this release: Kate extends a warm welcome, Dolphin offers you more choices, and a lot of apps serve up hamburgers galore!"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/announcements/gear/22.12.0.md:46
