#: content/announcements/gear/23.04.0.md:194
msgid "**[Kalendar](https://apps.kde.org/kalendar/)** is a modern and highly interactive calendaring and contact management app that works well on your computer and mobile phone. Kalendar has completely re-vamped its address book which is now more functional and easier to use."
