msgid "![](https://apps.kde.org/app-icons/org.kde.plasmatube.svg)"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/announcements/gear/23.04.0.md:206
msgid "[PlasmaTube](https://apps.kde.org/plasmatube)"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/announcements/gear/23.04.0.md:208
msgid "**[PlasmaTube](https://apps.kde.org/plasmatube/)** is a video player that allows you to stream YouTube videos directly to your desktop or phone. Apart from overhauling its looks, PlasmaTube now protects your privacy, as it accesses videos through [Invidious](https://github.com/iv-org/invidious), a YouTube frontend that does not require a login, blocks tracking and ads and does not require JavaScript."
