#. +> trunk5
#: content/announcements/gear/23.04.0.md:275
msgid "**[Dragon Player](https://apps.kde.org/dragonplayer/)** is a minimalistic KDE-native video and audio player. Dragon Player has undergone a major overhaul of its looks, including adopting the hamburger menu of many other KDE apps, and a welcome screen. It has also gained a streamlined and more intuitive set of default toolbar buttons."
