#. +> trunk5
#: content/announcements/gear/24.12.0/index.md:206
msgid "So you can travel further through the Fediverse, Tokodon has improved the support for alternative server implementations, such as GoToSocial, Iceshrimp.NET, and Pixelfed. Tokodon has also added \"News\" and \"Users\" tabs to the Explore page."
