#. +> trunk5
#: content/announcements/gear/24.12.0/index.md:208
msgid "![Tokodon guides you in your exploration of Mastodon.](tokodon_explore.png)"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/announcements/gear/24.12.0/index.md:210
msgid "We also added a new \"Following\" feed, to quickly page through your follows and their feeds. It's now easier to start private conversations or mention users right from their profile page."
