#. +> trunk5
#: content/announcements/gear/24.12.0/index.md:212
msgid "![Converse with your followers using private messages.](tokodon_following.png)"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/announcements/gear/24.12.0/index.md:214
msgid "Tokodon now supports quoting posts, and when you are writing a post, your user info is on display, which is useful if you post from multiple accounts. Right clicking on a link on a post will show a context menu allowing users to copy or share the URL directly."
