#. +> trunk5
#: content/announcements/gear/24.12.0/index.md:230
msgid "![NeoChat's improved emoji selector.](neochat_emojis.png)"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/announcements/gear/24.12.0/index.md:240
msgid "Instead of big features, devs have concentrated on the small things this time around, aiming to improve the overall experience. For example, Kate now starts up faster and gives visual cues of the Git status (\"modified\" or \"staged\") within the _Project_ tree."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/announcements/gear/24.12.0/index.md:245
