"an application for learning Japanese, has a search dialog in its Kanji Browser. [KWordQuiz](https://apps.kde.org/kwordquiz),\n"
"a flash card app, includes audio controls for your audio files. [Kalzium](https://apps.kde.org/kalzium)\n"
