#. +> trunk5
#: content/announcements/plasma/5/5.26.90.md:42
msgid "Behind the scenes <a href=\"https://notmart.org/blog/2022/12/multi-screen/\">there is a big multi-monitor revamp</a> to make working with screens much more reliable. There is also a new fine grained control tools when the user has 3 or more screens connected."
