msgid "One of the more spectacular (and useful) features added in Plasma 6.1 is that you can now start up a remote desktop directly from the *System Settings* app. This means that if you are sysadmin who needs to troubleshoot users' machines, or simply need to work on a Plasma-enabled computer that is out of reach, setting up a connection is just a few clicks away."
