#. +> trunk5
#: content/fundraisers/yearend2024.md:103
msgid "KDE is funded mainly by you: our friends, users, and supporters. Thanks to your donations, we can deliver the best free and open software that respects your privacy and gives you control over your devices and digital life. Your donations also help us keep tech corporations in check."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/fundraisers/yearend2024.md:105
msgid "By getting most of our support from people like you, we can preserve our independence and focus on developing what you need. We will never be pressured by any company to include the anti-features used in proprietary software that abuse your trust to maximize owners' profits."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/fundraisers/yearend2024.md:107
msgid "And that's how we like it. We really appreciate your support. Today, we want to show the world how you help keep Free Software projects alive and ethical!"
